  CM202:
    '🎉 Students and teachers LET’S LEARN TOGETHER 🎉\n\nHey language learners, did you know you can now invite teachers to help check your questions and exercises?! It’s true and starting from 8 Jun to 28 Jun, every Tuesday we will:\n\n \nShowcase the most helpful {language} teachers who’ve spent time answering questions and correcting posts. We’ll list the top 5 teachers and attach their profile links to the announcement, giving teachers a great chance to be seen.\n\nDraw out one {language} learner who has asked a question or completed an exercise and reward them with $5 italki Credits. The more you practice, the higher chance you have to hit the jackpot!',
