  HB071: 'Try my luck',
  HB072: 'Hint: The more tickets you enter, the higher your chances of winning.',
  HB073: 'Looks like you don’t have enough tickets. Don’t worry, you can earn tickets by completing more activities.',
  HB074: 'To find out if you’ve won a Lucky Draw, you can check “Draw History” the day after the draw.',
