  ILA068:
    'ACTFL is the American Council for Teaching Foreign Languages. The scale has 10 levels, from Novice, Low to Superior. This scale is used mostly in the US and Korea.',
  ILA069:
    'The IELTS is a standardized test used by many English-speaking universities to test non-native applicants. The speaking section ranges from 0 to 9.',
