  LH011:
    'Today, Benny is known throughout the language learning community as "the Irish Polyglot" and is famous for his many online videos that document his language learning adventures around the world. He runs the internet\'s biggest language learning blog, <a href="http://www.fluentin3months.com" target="_blank">www.fluentin3months.com</a>, and is the author of the bestselling book by the same name.',
