  LH041: 'JOIN THE #LANGUAGEHACKING COMMUNITY',
  LH042:
    'The #LanguageHacking community on italki allows you to learn from other language learners. Practice your language hacks in the community and get feedback from native speakers.',
  LH043: 'Exercises - Practice and improve your skills through audio and written exercises.',
