  MLP097:
    'Please read carefully the following Q&A to learn more about the prizes and to make sure you follow the steps to participate in the Giveaway',
  MLP098: 'How do I become eligible in the Giveaway? ',
  MLP099:
    'Users who have completed both steps #1 and #2 below will become eligible to win as participants of the Giveaway:',
  MLP100: '*MANDATORY STEP 1: Click on the "Enter Giveaway" button on this page and Sign up / Log in',
